###API 

##Tikkie
#Get Token:
POST
https://api-sandbox.abnamro.com/v1/oauth/token
Basic Authication: username:password
Body:
'Content-Type':'application/x-www-form-urlencoded'
grant_type: client_credentials
Scope: tikkie
https://api-sandbox.abnamro.com/v1/oauth/token

#Post Platform
POST
https://api-sandbox.abnamro.com/v1/tikkie/platforms
Headers: 
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Body:
'Content-Type': 'application/json'
{"name": "iou", "phoneNumber": "06XXXXXXXXX", "email": "XXXXXXXXXXXX@gmail.com", "notificationURL": "http://example.com"}
